erversion, using the webgui via URL ip_to_computer_B or 127.0.0.1:8384 everything works as expected (list opens and user can edit).\n\nSummary:\nits not possible to edit an Ignore Pattern list of another syncthing installation from another computer in the LAN. Only from the Computer, where the synthing installation is local.\nOther settings, such as File Versioning or Pull Order are editable.\n\nMy feature request:\nLet user change the whole configuration of syncthing from any computer.\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/1980/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/1980/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":1127512655,"node_id":"MDEyOkxhYmVsZWRFdmVudDExMjc1MTI2NTU=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/events/1127512655","actor":{"login":"st-review","id":16196517,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTk2NTE3","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/16196517?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review","html_url":"https://github.com/st-review","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/st-review/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"event":"labeled","commit_id":null,"comm